creator: Superior Grocers
descriptionHtml:
Superior Grocers is a chain of local, independent grocery stores. They have 40+ locations serving southern California communities.

Superior Grocers App is the easiest way for our loyal customers to receive savings and digital coupons every time they shop! The Superior Grocers App brings this all to your smartphone device with a simple and easy to use App. Along with notifications to alert you of new deals each week! Joining the programing is easy: simply Register or Log In, Add to List the coupons you want, and scan your phone at check out!
descriptionShort: The Superior Grocers App makes saving at the grocery store easy!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Optimised UI by adding a new feature "Manage Notification" in the profile page. 
- Now users will be asked permission to allow push messages as notification and we have handled push notification as per guidelines on android 13.
- Enabled guest user flow and delete account functionality as latest features.
